{"tid":2407640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2047何去何從？｜30000份地契到期 庫房耗盡埋炸彈 市民提早賣鋪賣樓","createTime":"2021-02-14T08:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T17:16:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d5bc75dd2bb412697dce3bd05cb4b92a135b82","tid":2407640,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FgB41ccoCfU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFgB41ccoCfU&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=bbc6a507\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FgB41ccoCfU</a><br />\n<br />\n在香港生活，總是離不開買樓。無論「上錯車」、「落錯車」、「創歷史新高」抑或「劈價成交」，所有樓都避不過一個議題：2047地契到期。全港約三萬份地契將於2047年6月30日期滿，大型藍籌屋苑如天水圍嘉湖山莊、美孚新邨、沙田第一城、藍田麗港城、將軍澳新都城，以及全港大部分住宅也無一倖免，就連骨灰龕位也面臨2047期滿。"},{"pid":"b7e23889da942605f6628b89bb4bc7f38a0e84b6","tid":2407640,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/66HFzD8t/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F66HFzD8t%2Fimage.jpg&h=1464e0b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c736e9ec7952428afef2784cf740e5d939299fe5","tid":2407640,"uid":259010,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:05:22.000Z","msg":"地稅=樓價100%  <br />\n<br />\n中共韮菜"},{"pid":"47617678b3dc5c37d81269da9ebaa52064d540b6","tid":2407640,"uid":30868,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"c736e9ec7952428afef2784cf740e5d939299fe5","tid":2407640,"uid":259010,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:05:22.000Z","msg":"地稅=樓價100%  <br />\n<br />\n中共韮菜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:08:56.000Z","msg":"而家個政府日日走出黎話窮到閪咁， 後生d 有生產力既就移民走哂， 中國輸入果班就個個公屋綜援， 仲有一大堆蝕錢大白象要養<br />\n2047 地價唔補足100% 呢個政府就財政崩潰架勒， 最多皇恩浩盪比你分十年補計番息， 續多50 年"},{"pid":"73d30b9b92f98023d1402f889d31c0168a702b86","tid":2407640,"uid":28397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"